evidence.source_document: Motion for a Preliminary Injunction and Memorandum of Points and Authorities in Support of Motion for a Preliminary Injunction
evidence.text: The dispute involves grant requirements and compliance with executive orders, not enforcement of a settlement agreement. The Motion for Preliminary Injunction seeks to prevent enforcement of new grant terms, not enforce an existing settlement. The Docket shows no motions to enforce settlements, only grant-related disputes and dismissal.
